'''''Sankofa'''''  ni filime yerekana ikinamico yakozwe [[Etiyopiya|na Etiyopiya yo mu]] 1993 iyobowe na Haile Gerima yibanze ku bucuruzi bw’abacakara bwa Atlantike<ref>https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/sankofa-movie-review-2021</ref> . Iyi nkuru igaragaramo Oyafunmike Ogunlano, Kofi Ghanaba, Mutabaruka, Alexandra Duah, na Afemo Omilami . Ijambo Sankofa ryakomotse ku rurimi rwa Akan rwo [[Gana|muri Gana]] risobanura "gusubira inyuma, gushaka, no kubona ubwenge, imbaraga n'ibyiringiro", nk'uko byavuzwe na Dr. Anna Julia Cooper<ref>https://www.indiewire.com/2021/09/sankofa-haile-gerima-interview-1234667076/</ref>.  Ijambo Sankofa ryibanda ku kamaro ko umuntu atagendera kure cyane ya kahise kugirango atere imbere ejo hazaza<ref>https://www.okayafrica.com/haile-gerima-sankofa-interview-array/</ref>. Muri filime, Sankofa agereranwa ninyoni n'indirimbo n'ingoma z'ingoma y'Imana<ref>https://www.washingtonian.com/2021/09/24/haile-gerimas-classic-film-sankofa-is-now-on-netflix-thanks-to-ava-duvernay/</ref>.  Filime ya Gerima yerekanye akamaro ko kutagira abantu bakomoka muri [[Afurika]] batandukana n’imizi yabo. Gerima yakoresheje urugendo rwimico Mona kugirango yerekane uburyo imyumvire nyafurika yerekana indangamuntu harimo kumenya imizi yumuntu no "gusubira aho yaturutse" (Gerima)<ref>https://www.cinema.ucla.edu/la-rebellion/films/sankofa</ref>.

== Umugambi ==
Filime itangirana numusaza Divine Drummer , Sankofa (yakinnye na Kofi Ghanaba ), akubita ingoma nyafurika aririmba imvugo ngo "Umwuka utinda w'abapfuye, haguruka<ref>https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-reviews/haile-gerima-sankofa-netlix-ava-duvernay-1235021486/</ref>." Ubu ni uburyo bwe bwo gushyikirana nabakurambere b'igihugu cya [[Afurika|Afrika]],  cyane [[Gana]]<ref>https://www.washingtonpost.com/entertainment/haile-gerima-sankofa-academy-museum/2021/09/23/baae53da-1c81-11ec-a99a-5fea2b2da34b_story.html</ref>. Yizera ko kuvuza ingoma ari ngombwa mu kugarura umwuka w'abakurambere be biciwe muri diaspora nyafurika<ref>https://www.nytimes.com/2021/10/15/movies/haile-gerima.html</ref> .  Inkuru ikomeza kugaragaza Mona (Oyafunmike Ogunlano), wabayeho [[Afurika]] na [[Amerika]] ntangarugero kuri film shoot muri [[Gana|Ghana]] <ref>https://www.becauseofthemwecan.com/blogs/culture/ava-duvernay-s-array-set-to-restore-re-release-legendary-filmmaker-haile-gerima-s-sankofa-on-netflix</ref>. Afite isomo ku Kigo cya Cape Coast, atazi ko cyakoreshejwe mu mateka mu bucuruzi bw’abacakara   kubera ko kuva kera atandukanijwe n’imizi [[Afurika|ye yo muri Afurika]]<ref>https://variety.com/2021/film/news/film-news-in-brief-sept-13-1235063603/</ref>[[Afurika|.]] Mugihe Mona ari kumurongo wicyitegererezo, ahura numusaza wamayobera Sankofa wavuzaga ingoma mugutangira film<ref>https://www.xartsplitta.net/en/filmscreening-sankofa-by-haile-gerima-for-sankofa-kita-berlin/</ref>. Sankofa akomeje kwibutsa Mona gusubira mu mateka ye kandi akaba umunyamahane cyane mu bijyanye no gukomeza ahantu h'abasekuruza bera<ref>https://aafilmfest.si.edu/discover/films/sankofa-1993</ref>, bityo agerageza kwirukana ba mukerarugendo b'abazungu mu kigo cy'abacakara.  Iyo Mona ingingo kujya A Kureba imbere castle ubwe,  Mona agerageza guhunga urugo rw'abacakara ahura na ba shebuja b'abaja bera agerageza gutekereza avuga ko akomoka muri [[Amerika]] kandi ko adakomoka muri [[Afurika]]<ref>https://www.africavenir.org/news-details/archive/2012/august/article/interview-with-haile-gerima-freedom-is-not-some-kind-of-unesco-milk-that-can-be-given-to-someo.html?tx_ttnews%255Bday%255D=20&cHash=1f144a60f7033edccd0c13eb466f5729</ref> . Ba shebuja b'abacakara ntibitaye ku byo Mona yavuze maze bamusunika ku muriro, bamwambura imyenda, bamushyira icyuma gishyushye ku mugongo<ref>https://www.events.sankofa.com/blank-2/sankofa-a-film-by-haile-gerima-shirt</ref>.

